      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's built to last! This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it, making it the perfect choice for someone looking for a solid, reliable vehicle. While it shows some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a hardworking companion ready for its next adventure!",
