    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
