    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest standards of excellence. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, recently enhanced by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather bolsters show no wear, the electronics are crisp, and the interior retains that unmistakable new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with every service record meticulously organized in a binder. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory\u2014tight, responsive, and powerful. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
